{"tid":532841,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 李嘉欣孖囝囝玩轉嘉年華","createTime":"2018-01-18T08:18:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T16:42:53.000Z","uid":48905,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9df0daa5cd15bb9008a54d9f897aae4fd77fa334","tid":532841,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"不經不覺，原來許晉亨與李嘉欣結婚已有10年，他們的囝囝Jayden下個月就7歲。李嘉欣與囝囝一向關係親密，昨日嘉欣就帶Jayden去嘉年華玩，更將二人的合照放上社交網與網友開心share！其中一張Jayden與媽咪緊緊擁抱，Jayden已經長到媽咪膊頭位高。另一張就是嘉欣的單獨照，戴著Cap帽的她向著鏡頭攤開雙手，笑得非常燦爛，嘉欣亦開心留言：「好似人地王晶咁癡心情長劍咁，可以樣樣野都為晒邱淑貞去做，咁樣做對於你來講係侮辱你既智慧係戇居丫嘛。」，看來非常享受這天的親子活動！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/18/161717_1921d932a74d0f9c86ab5036db308161.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F18%2F161717_1921d932a74d0f9c86ab5036db308161.png&h=03fc2cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"> 大美人李嘉欣非常享受這天的親子活動！</span>"},{"pid":"5a5fd8c32cb0c33c8730adb62cb233e68d258185","tid":532841,"uid":154907,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"洪欣呢？"},{"pid":"dd23254aa31229c0af9839d4dad27d393704fc11","tid":532841,"uid":125061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:24:20.000Z","msg":"我真係恭喜"},{"pid":"ef24f00da47353321a459cbd2199673ce36a3e9d","tid":532841,"uid":118973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"快撚d捧紅個囝囝"},{"pid":"4fe502a2a1b45e07aaa53949a2aad8a698973ced","tid":532841,"uid":42009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef24f00da47353321a459cbd2199673ce36a3e9d","tid":532841,"uid":118973,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"快撚d捧紅個囝囝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji